{==============================================================
RPC [TIU DOCUMENTS BY CONTEXT] returns
the following string '^' pieces:
===============================================================
      1 -  Document IEN
      2 -  Document Title
      3 -  FM date of document
      4 -  Patient Name
      5 -  DUZ;Author name
      6 -  Location
      7 -  Status
